metadata.name: WAR - SUPPORT UKRAINE
metadata.description:
War has crushed Ukrainian's lives, destroyed cities and communities. We stand infringed, but not broken. This art lives to spread the word and express feelings of those suffering from conflict.

Contributor will receive a physical copy of the T-shirt worn by Digital Resistance division of Ukraine. 
[See a photo in war.fusion instagram](https://www.instagram.com/p/ChZj_lmIrh7/)

#russiaisaterroriststate #warforua
